Source Code

These source-code files were transcribed from the Raytheon document "FINAL REPORT: AUXILIARY MEMORY FOR APOLLO GUIDANCE COMPUTER CONTRACT NAS 9-5994". The report was obtained from archive.org mirrors of the NASA Techincal Reports Server (NTRS). The report can be found here and the appendix containing the listing can be found here. Report any problems by creating "issues" at the Virtual AGC Project's GitHub Repository.

Notations on the program listing read, in part:
